        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Chermside property values are driven by proximity to Westfield Chermside, access to Prince Charles Hospital for healthcare workers, and the suburb's position as the northern corridor's major retail and services hub. Homes on quiet internal streets away from Gympie Road attract a strong family buyer pool, while properties near the hospital and shopping precinct draw professionals and investors seeking good rental yield.</p>
