          <span style="color:#c4912a; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Well-priced Chermside homes typically sell within 25 to 40 days. The suburb draws buyers from across the northern corridor, particularly families attracted by retail convenience and young professionals connected to Prince Charles Hospital. Buyer competition is active year-round, with the strongest periods through autumn and spring.</p>
